      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t小米对标的是Tesla而且现在这个定价根本不赚钱 起步价都不赚钱 雷布斯是打算靠卖周边赚钱还是靠涨价赚钱 不看好小米汽车<br/>\n<br/>\n* Xiaomi CEO Lei Jun said the standard version of the SU7 will sell for 215,900 yuan ($30,408) in the country — a price he acknowledged would mean the company was selling each car at a loss.<br/>\n* Tesla’s Model 3 starts at 245,900 yuan in China.<br/>\n* Lei claimed the standard version of the SU7 beat the Model 3 on more than 90% of its specifications, except on two aspects that he said it might take Xiaomi at least three to five years to catch up with Tesla on.\t\t</div>",
